Name: Brisbane
Description: The Division of Brisbane consists of part of the Brisbane City Council.
ProductsAndIndustry: The area is mostly residential but contains some light industry. It includes the Queensland Parliament House and Brisbane City Council Chambers. Many Commonwealth Government, State Government and business administrative offices are found in the area.
NameDerivation: Named in recognition of the City of Brisbane.
